snippet.textDisplay:
I was at a glass blowing thing when my family were at our usual cabin in Denmark (we're Norwegian), and they showed us the whole process first, then let us do it one at a time. They showed one more time again one to one, gave us all the power and guided us through it. We were gonna make a big glass ball with whatever colour you wanted. They were really good at teaching and guiding us. They made it fun too. Also, we actually got to blow the ball ourselves. 😅

This guy sounds like a cool dude, he's good at his job and all, but maybe not an amazing teacher. XD
